WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:28.000
Customer request flow: A pending request exists and the customer has a booking code plus a confirmation link.

00:00:28.000 --> 00:02:17.000
Customer verification and approval gate: The signed agreement and insurance choice are saved, and payment remains locked until admin approval.

00:02:17.000 --> 00:02:34.520
Customer payment after approval: The approved booking is paid and moves to the paid/confirmed lifecycle.
